希望能够请教一下各位的意见，小弟先在此谢过了。</p>\n", "last_modified": 1627115773, "replies": 56, "id": 791522}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/e7b2/4b11/360_large.png?m=1583044904", "name": "windows", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/e7b2/4b11/360_normal.png?m=1583044904", "title": "Windows", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/windows", "topics": 2140, "footer": "", "header": "Windows, not walls.", "title_alternative": "Windows", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/e7b2/4b11/360_mini.png?m=1583044904", "stars": 711, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 360, "parent_node_name": "os"}, "member": {"username": "baoshuo", "website": "baoshuo.ren", "github": "renbaoshuo", "psn": "", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/6bd5/cf64/486502_mini.png?m=1613975558", "bio": "🇨🇳 15 y.o. / Student & Developer & OIer / GitHub: https://github.com/renbaoshuo / AS141776 / Blog: https://blog.baoshuo.ren / Website: https://baoshuo.ren", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/baoshuo", "tagline": "", "twitter": "renbaoshuo", "created": 1587960878, "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/6bd5/cf64/486502_mini.png?m=1613975558", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/6bd5/cf64/486502_mini.png?m=1613975558", "location": "Shijiazhuang, China", "btc": "", "id": 486502}, "last_reply_by": "Oceanhime", "last_touched": 1627147942, "title": "没忍住，把主力机的系统升到了 Win 11（附图）", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/791479", "created": 1627095816, "content": "## 前言\r\n\r\n个人实测升级需要半个多小时，截至发帖时需要切换到 Dev 频道（即 Fast Ring ）获取更新。\r\n\r\n## 展示图\r\n\r\n![]( https://vip2.loli.io/2021/07/24/1ig3u7FqCRT9VJp.png)\r\n\r\n↑ 桌面及任务栏 （迫真 Macindows ）\r\n\r\n![]( https://vip2.loli.io/2021/07/24/rsnYAa4yKe97LiQ.png)\r\n\r\n↑ 文件资源管理器（左边可以直接看到 WSL 文件系统的入口了，不用再敲 `\\\\wsl$\\Ubuntu` 了）\r\n\r\n![]( https://vip1.loli.io/2021/07/24/6MLKYyUmS2oVrAN.png)\r\n\r\n↑ 系统版本\r\n\r\n![]( https://vip2.loli.io/2021/07/24/NY5TfiWsVvJC3Do.png)\r\n\r\n↑ 设置\r\n\r\n![]( https://vip2.loli.io/2021/07/24/Fg8LutnGIyY41OR.png)\r\n\r\n\r\n↑ 开始菜单\r\n\r\n![]( https://vip2.loli.io/2021/07/24/3rcRHelG7I9KWi5.png)\r\n\r\n↑ 任务管理器界面没有太大变化\r\n\r\n![]( https://vip2.loli.io/2021/07/24/UCrRmfD346nNzgc.png)\r\n\r\n↑ 右键菜单\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n其他的等以后有时间了再补充吧。\r\n\r\n## 已知问题\r\n\r\n这是我使用时遇到的一些问题 / 感觉不舒服的地方\r\n\r\n+ [UAC 弹窗翻译错误]( https://aka.ms/AAda1wm)\r\n+ 窗口的圆角有锯齿\r\n+ 微信 / QQ / TIM 等腾讯系软件最小化没有动画效果\r\n+ 动态磁贴没了\r\n+ 仍然没有旗帜类表情\r\n\r\n待补充...\r\n\r\n## 后记\r\n\r\n![]( https://vip2.loli.io/2021/07/24/sVHSC13iQE45TOy.png)\r\n\r\n（话说像我这种只体验不反馈的人是不是就算在浪费微软服务器带宽啊", "content_rendered": "<h2>前言</h2>\n<p>个人实测升级需要半个多小时，截至发帖时需要切换到 Dev 频道（即 Fast Ring ）获取更新。</p>\n<h2>展示图</h2>\n<p><img alt=\"\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://vip2.loli.io/2021/07/24/1ig3u7FqCRT9VJp.png\"/></p>\n<p>↑ 桌面及任务栏 （迫真 Macindows ）</p>\n<p><img alt=\"\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://vip2.loli.io/2021/07/24/rsnYAa4yKe97LiQ.png\"/></p>\n<p>↑ 文件资源管理器（左边可以直接看到 WSL 文件系统的入口了，不用再敲 <code>\\\\wsl$\\Ubuntu</code> 了）</p>\n<p><img alt=\"\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://vip1.loli.io/2021/07/24/6MLKYyUmS2oVrAN.png\"/></p>\n<p>↑ 系统版本</p>\n<p><img alt=\"\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://vip2.loli.io/2021/07/24/NY5TfiWsVvJC3Do.png\"/></p>\n<p>↑ 设置</p>\n<p><img alt=\"\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://vip2.loli.io/2021/07/24/Fg8LutnGIyY41OR.png\"/></p>\n<p>↑ 开始菜单</p>\n<p><img alt=\"\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://vip2.loli.io/2021/07/24/3rcRHelG7I9KWi5.png\"/></p>\n<p>↑ 任务管理器界面没有太大变化</p>\n<p><img alt=\"\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://vip2.loli.io/2021/07/24/UCrRmfD346nNzgc.png\"/></p>\n<p>↑ 右键菜单</p>\n<hr/>\n<p>其他的等以后有时间了再补充吧。</p>\n<h2>已知问题</h2>\n<p>这是我使用时遇到的一些问题 / 感觉不舒服的地方</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://aka.ms/AAda1wm\" rel=\"nofollow\">UAC 弹窗翻译错误</a></li>\n<li>窗口的圆角有锯齿</li>\n<li>微信 / QQ / TIM 等腾讯系软件最小化没有动画效果</li>\n<li>动态磁贴没了</li>\n<li>仍然没有旗帜类表情</li>\n</ul>\n<p>待补充...</p>\n<h2>后记</h2>\n<p><img alt=\"\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://vip2.loli.io/2021/07/24/sVHSC13iQE45TOy.png\"/></p>\n<p>（话说像我这种只体验不反馈的人是不是就算在浪费微软服务器带宽啊</p>\n", "last_modified": 1627095924, "replies": 46, "id": 791479}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_large.png?m=1626793722", "name": "programmer", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_normal.png?m=1626793722", "title": "程序员", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/programmer", "topics": 45120, "footer": "", "header": "While code monkeys are not eating bananas, they're coding.", "title_alternative": "Programmer", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_mini.png?m=1626793722", "stars": 7444, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 300, "parent_node_name": "computer"}, "member": {"username": "shishirui", "website": null, "github": null, "psn": null, "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/a774/3181/68275_mini.png?m=1405903206", "bio": null, "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/shishirui", "tagline": null, "twitter": null, "created": 1405607007, "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/a774/3181/68275_mini.png?m=1405903206", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/a774/3181/68275_mini.png?m=1405903206", "location": null, "btc": null, "id": 68275}, "last_reply_by": "whywaoxaks", "last_touched": 1627178666, "title": "为了管住忍不住刷抖音的手，本程序员用了这个办法，非常有效，推荐大家试试", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/791557", "created": 1627140418, "content": "在 iOS 上的「屏幕使用时间」中设置「抖音」每天只能刷 30 分钟，并且设置一个自己都不知道的密码！\r\n\r\n不知道是不是对自己狠了点\r\n\r\n![]( https://tva1.sinaimg.cn/large/008i3skNly1gss